                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Abiogenesis: Solar Isotoma"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. </p><p>If Solar Isotoma is on the field, deals +2 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/42d2ae5af0169e6938febe18de57d31a_1839574548734686575.png",
                "id": "talent12457",
                "key": "Rite of Progeniture: Tectonic Tide",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rite of Progeniture: Tectonic Tide"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When you perform \"Switch Character\" and this Summon is on the field:</span> This switch is considered a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fast Action</span> instead of a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Combat Action</span>. (Once per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1a3db5c5531fb4444758f49100411b27_4689709534301462035.png",
                "id": "talent19474",
                "key": "Solar Isotoma",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/27/35428890/02297af9d3309f3e4e40eca8911a19f6_2217899216136196852.png",
                "title": "Solar Isotoma"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/d5cff14cce456ddfc98dd4b238e7159c_3684416353399803965.png",
                "id": "talent53758",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Fast Action</span></strong><br>You can continue with other actions after conducting 1 Fast Action.<br>Only after conducting 1 Combat Action will the turn pass over to your opponent.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Combat Action</span></strong><br>After you finish 1 Combat Action, it will be your opponent's turn.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Playing a card from your Hand with this rule is also a Combat Action rather than a Fast Action</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1fafbff4b60b57a39c1f9a8c226a3a6b_430026298312662124.png",
                "id": "talent11464",
